Sabelo Mlangeni (amụrụ n'ubochí irí abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 1980) bụ onye na-ese foto South Africa bi ma na-arụ ọrụ na Johannesburg, South Africa. A na-enwe ọrụ ya na nchịkọta nke Art Institute of Chicago, San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, na Walther Collection.
A mụrụ Sabelo Mlangeni n'afọ 1980 na Driefontein, obodo dị nso na Wakkerstroom na Mpumalanga, South Africa.
